            <INFO_ADD>
               <P>1) Register your company on the eTenderWales portal (this is only required once):</P>
               <P>— Navigate to the portal: http://etenderwales.bravosolution.co.uk</P>
               <P>— Click the “Suppliers register here” link,</P>
               <P>— Enter your correct business and user details,</P>
